<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11239</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17448</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西必须赶到美罗城造币厂。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17449</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19720</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>幽灵强盗在那里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19721</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21843</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她必须抓住他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21844</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25692</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗨！”罗西对朋友们说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25693</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28334</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我想我得回家了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28335</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33228</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我......嗯......有点不舒服。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33229</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40383</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯。”罗西离开后，特勒尔说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40384</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44026</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“难怪她看起来有些不高兴。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44027</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51076</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西很快就到了美罗城造币厂。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51077</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54834</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>警察包围了整栋大楼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54835</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61240</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探向罗西招手。她飞了下去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61241</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66489</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是为幽灵强盗准备的惊喜派对吗？”罗西问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66490</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69799</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探皱了皱眉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69800</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72708</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不，这不是一个派对。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72709</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76187</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我只是开个玩笑。”罗西说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76188</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78777</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那他现在在哪里？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78778</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83456</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“幽灵强盗还在造币厂里。”侦探说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83457</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86441</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是，我们不知道他在哪儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86442</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89273</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>因为他是隐形的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89274</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93469</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西点点头。“他很难抓到。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93470</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100314</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>今天早上，我差点儿就抓到他了，但是他逃走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100315</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105732</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家都以为我在毁灭美罗城呢。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105733</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我明白。”史密斯侦探说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108986</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113629</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们需要尽快抓到他。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113630</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117900</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的，尽快。”罗西说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117901</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121563</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“大家开始把我当坏人看了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121564</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128605</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“要是我们能知道他是怎么隐形的就好了。”史密斯侦探说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128606</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134170</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西想了想。“他一定有一件特殊的衣服。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134171</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137448</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我不相信他是真正的幽灵。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137449</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142797</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你不相信？”史密斯侦探怀疑地问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142798</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148595</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的。”罗西说，“真正的幽灵能穿透墙壁。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148596</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152804</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，这个坏人是从门进去的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152805</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156783</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你说得对。”史密斯侦探说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156784</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160595</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西向大楼走了几步。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160596</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164327</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我用我的超级听力试试。”她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164328</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168309</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“也许我能听到幽灵强盗在哪里。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168310</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172532</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西闭上眼睛，仔细听。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172533</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176691</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她听到了办公室风扇转动的声音，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176692</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183583</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小虫子在走廊飞舞的声音，还有脚步声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>183584</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186648</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西猛地睁开眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186649</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190051</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我听到了。他在走路！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190052</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193717</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西迅速飞进造币厂，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200042</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>跟着脚步声来到一个堆满钱的大房间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200043</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204310</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>钱币整齐地排成几行。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204311</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207996</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>看上去少了一部分钱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207997</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212122</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西走到钱堆中间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212123</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216313</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“幽灵强盗在哪里呢？”她想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216314</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219948</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西再一次仔细地听。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219949</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222731</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她听到了呼吸声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222732</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226967</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“喂，幽灵强盗！”罗西大叫，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>226968</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229523</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我知道你在这里！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229524</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236846</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“呜！”一个声音喊道，并大笑起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236847</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240395</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西飞到钱堆上面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240396</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245023</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她看了看四周，但是没有看到任何人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245024</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249115</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我穿着隐形衣。”那个声音说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>249116</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>256575</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你绝对找不到我！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>